##Content Summary##

#####Front#####
The agrement of the holye Fathers, and Doctors of the churche, vpon the cheifeſt articles of Chriſti
1. ¶ The contentes of the boke.

1. ¶ To the mooſt excellente and vertuous Princeſſes Quene Marye, wyfe to oure mooſte ſoueraynge Lorde, Philip by the grace of God. &c. Iohn Aungell, one of youre graces chaplyns of youre honourable Chappel, wiſſheth perpetuall felicitie, not only in this worlde, but alſo in the worlde to come.
